Comparison of the double flowers of 
<taxonomicName id="4C2A4D53FFA8FF9AFDA78E132E821D36" authority="' Sunny" authorityName="Sunny" box="[628,955,1284,1305]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="8" pageNumber="233" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="porphyrocalyx">
<emphasis id="B95EEAC2FFA8FF9AFDA78E132E561D36" box="[628,879,1284,1305]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="233">Kalanchoe porphyrocalyx</emphasis>
‘Sunny
