Balloon’ and the regular ones of 
<taxonomicName id="4C2A4D53FFA8FF9AFAD08E122C051D12" authorityName="Humbert ex Smith &amp; Figueiredo" authorityYear="2019" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="8" pageNumber="233" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="porphyrocalyx" variety="sambiranensis">
<emphasis id="B95EEAC2FFA8FF9AFAD08E1228921D36" box="[1283,1451,1284,1306]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="233">K. porphyrocalyx</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B95EEAC2FFA8FF9AFF628E3F2C051D12" box="[177,316,1320,1341]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="233">sambiranensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Photograph: Gideon F. Smith.
</paragraph>
